      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation. This masterfully maintained vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition, representing the absolute gold standard for pre-owned quality. From its mirror-finish exterior to its factory-fresh interior, every detail has been preserved with uncompromising care. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to secure a true investment-grade vehicle that performs as flawlessly as it looks.",
