    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine gliding through the city at dusk, the moonlight dancing across the hand-polished curves of this midnight-blue masterpiece. Inside, you are enveloped in the rich, buttery aroma of hand-stitched leather that feels like a second skin. Every turn of the key awakens a mechanical symphony\u2014a purr so smooth it whispers of open highways and secret coastal escapes. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved moment in time, a sanctuary of elegance that commands the road with a silent, confident grace. It waits for a driver who understands that some legends don't age; they simply wait for their next great chapter.",
      "price": 48500.0,
