      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like my own child\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed every single weekend. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape, inside and out; you won't find a smoother drive or a cleaner interior anywhere else in the neighborhood. It\u2019s basically showroom quality and ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved!",
